Installation:

  git clone git@github.com:dshrader38/dot-files.git ~/dot-files

Create symlinks:

  ln -fs ~/dot-files/.vim ~/.vim
  ln -fs ~/dot-files/.vimrc ~/.vimrc
  ln -fs ~/dot-files/.bashrc ~/.bashrc
  ln -fs ~/dot-files/.bash_profile ~/.bash_profile
  ln -fs ~/dot-files/.gitconfig ~/.gitconfig
  ln -fs ~/fot-files/.gitignore_global ~/.gitignore_global 
  ln -fs ~/dot-files/.ssh ~/.ssh

Set the git global ignore file:
  git config --global core.excludesfile '~/.gitignore_global`' 
  git config --get core.excludesfile

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

  cd ~/dot-files
  git submodule init
  git submodule update

Change permissions on .ssh files (if necessary):
  chmod 600 .ssh/id_rsa
  chmod 644 .ssh/id_rsa.pub
